20 prior to that date. Subsection (g) of this section becomes effective October 1, 2025, and shall not
21 affect the determination of whether a violation of G.S. 20-24.1 prior to that date constituted a
22 motor vehicle moving offense. Subsection (h) of this section becomes effective October 1, 2025,
23 and does not apply to registration renewals withheld for a failure to appear in court or a failure
24 to pay fines or costs that occurred prior to that date. Subsections (i) and (j) of this section become
25 effective October 1, 2025, and apply to license reinstatements on or after that date. The remainder
26 of this section is effective when it becomes law.
